::Striker::

Striker sits down on a boulder. His scanners had detected two bots off in the 
mountains. One had a predacon signature and the other was neither predacon 
nor maximal. Thinking it oveer, he decides to go on into the mountains toward 
the two bots. He figured his chances were better with bots than damaged and 
in the middle of no where. He proceeds toward the mountains.
